ers firsthand.</p>\n<p>Through company sessions and networking at the meeting points throughout the day, you will learn about the core business of participating companies and have the opportunity to network directly with the recruiters making your pitch. Take the chance to interview with companies looking for the best fitting talent!</p>\n<p class=\"highlight\">ESADE Career Services is looking forward to meeting you at this recruiting event!</p>\n<div>\n</div></div>\";s:12:\"safe_summary\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:11:\"field_image\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:13:{s:3:\"fid\";s:2:\"18\";s:3:\"uid\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"filename\";s:14:\"mba-whatis.jpg\";s:3:\"uri\";s:23:\"public://mba-whatis.jpg\";s:8:\"filemime\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:8:\"filesize\";s:6:\"132387\";s:6:\"status\";s:1:\"1\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1417341255\";s:11:\"rdf_mapping\";a:0:{}s:3:\"alt\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"464\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"312\";}}}}',0,1417514515,1),('field:node:5','a:2:{s:4:\"body\";a:1:{s:3:\"und\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:5:\"value\";s:848:\"<div class=\"contents_txt\"><p><span class=\"highlight_regular\">Company Sessions:</span> Classrooms ESADE Creapolis (2nd and 3rd floor, module D)</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"highlight_regular\">Interviews:</span> ESADE Creapolis (1st, 2nd and 3rd floor, module D)</p>\r\n<p><span class=\"highlight_regular\">Meeting Points:</span>&nbsp;ESADE Creapolis (2nd and 3rd floor, module D). An excellent opportunity to visit personally the company representatives during the time slot allocated in the agenda and present yourself to clarify any doubts you might have as well as leave a great impression of yourself to the recruiters.</p>\r\n<p>Keep in mind that you should not occupy the recruiter for more than 10 minutes and that recruiters are instructed to invite you to an informal interview after 17:00 hrs in case they found your profiles of interest!&nbsp;</p><div>\";s:7:\"summary\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"format\";s:9:\"full_html\";s:10:\"safe_value\";